---
import PortalLayout from '../layouts/PortalLayout.astro';
---

<PortalLayout title="Design Library" mainBg="#fef2f2">
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@400;600;700&family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,600&family=Source+Sans+3:wght@400;600&family=Bricolage+Grotesque:opsz,wght@12..96,600;12..96,800&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:opsz,wght@9..40,400;9..40,500;9..40,600&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@600;700;800&family=Syne:wght@700;800&family=Archivo+Black&family=Archivo:wght@400;500;700&family=Cormorant:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </Fragment>

  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Design Library</h1>
    <p>7 style packages · 21 color palettes — pre-built design systems for every Spirit Media site</p>
  </div>

  <div class="intro-card">
    <p>Each package defines fonts, colors, button styles, and component patterns. When starting a new site, tell Claude:<br>
    <strong>"Build [Site Name] using Style Package: Herald."</strong> &nbsp;Or mix packages and palettes:<br>
    <strong>"Use Still Waters with the Midnight Forest palette."</strong></p>
  </div>

  <!-- TOC -->
  <div class="toc-row">
    <a href="#herald" class="toc-pill">01 Herald</a>
    <a href="#torch" class="toc-pill">02 Torch</a>
    <a href="#still-waters" class="toc-pill">03 Still Waters</a>
    <a href="#cornerstone" class="toc-pill">04 Cornerstone</a>
    <a href="#radiance" class="toc-pill">05 Radiance</a>
    <a href="#signal" class="toc-pill">06 Signal</a>
    <a href="#summit" class="toc-pill">07 Summit</a>
    <a href="#palettes" class="toc-pill toc-pill-accent">+ 21 Palettes</a>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-6">

    <!-- ===== 01 HERALD ===== -->
    <section class="pkg-card" id="herald">
      <div class="pkg-meta" style="background:#EDE8DF;">
        <div class="pkg-num" style="color:#B8922A;">01 · Herald</div>
        <div class="pkg-title" style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:2.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#1C1A17;line-height:1.05;">Herald</div>
        <p class="pkg-desc" style="font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;color:#6B6359;">Warm editorial authority. Publishing, Bible translation, theological teaching, authorship.</p>
        <div class="pkg-best-label" style="color:#B8922A;">Best for</div>
        <p class="pkg-best" style="font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;color:#6B6359;">Publishing · Bible projects · Author sites · Theological teaching</p>
        <div class="swatches">
          <div class="swatch-row"><div class="swatch" style="background:#FAF7F2;border:1px solid #D9D2C8;"></div><div><span class="swatch-name" style="color:#1C1A17;font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;">Cream</span><span class="swatch-hex">#FAF7F2</span></div></div>
          <div class="swatch-row"><div class="swatch" style="background:#EDE8DF;"></div><div><span class="swatch-name" style="color:#1C1A17;font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;">Parchment</span><span class="swatch-hex">#EDE8DF</span></div></div>
          <div class="swatch-row"><div class="swatch" style="background:#1C1A17;"></div><div><span class="swatch-name" style="color:#1C1A17;font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;">Ink</span><span class="swatch-hex">#1C1A17</span></div></div>
          <div class="swatch-row"><div class="swatch" style="background:#B8922A;"></div><div><span class="swatch-name" style="color:#1C1A17;font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;">Gold</span><span class="swatch-hex">#B8922A</span></div></div>
          <div class="swatch-row"><div class="swatch" style="background:#6B6359;"></div><div><span class="swatch-name" style="color:#1C1A17;font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;">Warm Gray</span><span class="swatch-hex">#6B6359</span></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="pkg-fonts">
          <span style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:#1C1A17;">Cormorant Garamond</span>
          <span style="font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;font-size:0.8rem;color:#6B6359;">Source Sans 3</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pkg-preview" style="background:#FAF7F2;">
        <div>
          <div class="preview-label" style="color:#B8922A;font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;">Typography</div>
          <div style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:3rem;font-weight:700;color:#1C1A17;line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-.02em;">The Word <em style="font-style:italic;color:#B8922A;">Endures</em><br>Forever</div>
          <div style="margin-top:0.625rem;font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;font-size:0.9375rem;color:#6B6359;line-height:1.7;">We equip Kingdom Messengers with tools to carry God's word to the ends of the earth.</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="preview-label" style="color:#B8922A;font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;">Buttons</div>
          <div class="btn-row">
            <span class="prev-btn" style="background:#B8922A;color:#FAF7F2;font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;font-size:0.6875rem;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;border-radius:2px;">Begin Your Journey</span>
            <span class="prev-btn" style="background:transparent;color:#B8922A;font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;font-size:0.6875rem;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;border-radius:2px;border:1px solid #B8922A;">Learn More</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="preview-label" style="color:#B8922A;font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;">Card</div>
          <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #D9D2C8;padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;border-radius:4px;max-width:380px;">
            <div style="font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;font-size:0.625rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.13em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8922A;margin-bottom:0.375rem;">Publishing</div>
            <div style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.3125rem;font-weight:600;color:#1C1A17;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:0.4375rem;">From Manuscript to Ministry Impact</div>
            <div style="font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;font-size:0.84375rem;color:#6B6359;line-height:1.65;">Our publishing process walks alongside authors from first draft to marketplace.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

