        <p class="pkg-desc" style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;color:#A1A1AA;">Bold apostolic urgency. Global missions, prophetic media, training networks, movements.</p>
        <div class="pkg-best-label" style="color:#F59E0B;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;">Best for</div>
        <p class="pkg-best" style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;color:#A1A1AA;">Global missions · Apostolic networks · Leadership training · Movements</p>
        <div class="swatches">
          <div class="swatch-row"><div class="swatch" style="background:#09090B;border:1px solid #27272A;"></div><div><span class="swatch-name" style="color:#FAFAFA;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;">Void</span><span class="swatch-hex" style="color:#A1A1AA;">#09090B</span></div></div>
