        <div>
          <div class="preview-label" style="color:#6B7280;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;">Typography</div>
          <div style="font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:3rem;color:#2C2C2C;line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-.01em;">Lead from the <em style="font-style:italic;color:#4E6B5E;">Inside</em><br>Out</div>
          <div style="margin-top:0.625rem;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:0.9375rem;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.75;">A 12-month leadership intensive for those ready to lead from wholeness, not wounds.</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="preview-label" style="color:#6B7280;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;">Buttons</div>
